  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Explorer Title</span>, commemorating completion of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Blighted</span> expedition, the glorious retrieval of ill-gotten lucre, and the discovery of a pirate secret.<br><br>Apply this title to your banner at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探险家头衔</span>，纪念你完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">瘟疫侵扰</span>远征，光荣地追回不义之财并发现了一个海盗的秘密。<br><br>请使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>在你的旗帜上应用此头衔。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險家頭銜</span>，紀念<span class=\"name name-stellar\">「毀滅殆盡」</span>探險的完成、獲取不義之財的榮耀，以及海盜秘密的發現。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>將此頭銜套用至旗幟上。"
  },
